snippet: South Korean officials on Thursday criticized a North Korean artillery launch that they say happened minutes before a Chinese commercial plane reportedly carrying 202 people flew in the same area....

headline.print_headline: Seoul: NK Artillery Launched Near Chinese Flight
headline.main: Seoul: NK Artillery Launched Near Chinese Flight

lead_paragraph: South Korean officials on Thursday criticized a North Korean artillery launch that they say happened minutes before a Chinese commercial plane reportedly carrying 202 people flew in the same area.
